Class SubtypeGraphTraverser<T>

java.lang.Object
gw.api.graph.traverse.GraphTraverserBase<T>
gw.api.graph.traverse.SubtypeGraphTraverser<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
GraphTraverser<T>
public abstract class SubtypeGraphTraverser<T> extends GraphTraverserBase<T>
Specialized graph traverser for traversing types. This implementation takes into account any subtypes of the currently traversed node, and traverses those as well.
